item.title: Need someone to teamview me and help my server become online IP Problems
item.dc:creator: @durial12 durial12
item.description:
@durial12 wrote:

Hello.

  1. Have you properly portforwarded port 43594 on your router? If your router can’t, then yes, you will need uTorrent if you want to portforward. Also make sure you portforwarded to the ip of your computer (I.E 192.168.1.xxx)

  2. Have you got a no-ip?

  3. Ask a friend to try and log in with the no-ip, sometimes they can use it and you cant, but you can use 0.0.0.0.

Hope this helps

Durial
